  "keyFeatures": [
    "Jetpack Compose mental model mapped to Svelte — familiar API for Android developers",
    "Immutable, chainable Modifier system for declarative layout and styling",
    "Layout components: Column, Row, Box, Scaffold, LazyColumn, LazyRow",
    "Structural motion with AnimatedVisibility and AnimatedContent",
    "Compose-like navigation with NavController, NavHost, and back-stack management",
    "Material 3-inspired theming with ColorScheme, Typography, Shapes, and Spacing tokens",
    "Light/dark/system theme modes via ComposeTheme provider",
    "Rich UI components: Button variants, Cards, TextFields, Menus, Icon, Image",
    "ContentScale enum for image scaling (Crop, Fit, FillBounds, etc.)",
    "Type-safe Alignment and Arrangement tokens",
    "No virtual DOM abstractions — built directly on Svelte 5",
    "CSS baseline contract for deterministic layout behavior"
  ],
